tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE customers (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    name VARCHAR(50),
    email VARCHAR(100),
    phone_number VARCHAR(15),
    purchase_history JSON
)

CREATE TABLE Customer (
    customer_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    name VARCHAR(50),
    email VARCHAR(100),
    phone_number VARCHAR(15)
);

CREATE TABLE PurchaseHistory (
    purchase_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id INT,
    purchase_date DATE,
    item_name VARCHAR(100),
    quantity INT,
    price DECIMAL(10, 2),
    FOREIGN KEY (customer_id) REFERENCES Customer(customer_id)
);

CREATE TABLE Bicycles (
    bicycle_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    bicycle_brand VARCHAR(50),
    bicycle_model VARCHAR(50),
    bicycle_price DECIMAL(10, 2),
    quantity_available INT
);

CREATE TABLE PurchaseHistory (
    purchase_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id INT,
    bicycle_id INT,
    purchase_date DATE,
    purchase_amount DECIMAL(10, 2),
    FOREIGN KEY (customer_id) REFERENCES Customers(customer_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (bicycle_id) REFERENCES Bicycles(bicycle_id)
);

CREATE TABLE contact_info (
  contact_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  customer_id INT NOT NULL,
  address VARCHAR(255),
  city VARCHAR(100),
  state VARCHAR(50),
  postal_code VARCHAR(10)
);

CREATE TABLE bicycles (
  bicycle_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  brand VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  model VARCHAR(50),
  year INT,
  price DECIMAL(10, 2)
);

CREATE TABLE purchase_history (
  purchase_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  customer_id INT NOT NULL,
  bicycle_id INT NOT NULL,
  purchase_date DATE,
  quantity INT
);

CREATE TABLE customers (
    customer_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    first_name VARCHAR(50),
    last_name VARCHAR(50),
    email VARCHAR(100),
    phone_number VARCHAR(20)
);

CREATE TABLE addresses (
    address_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id INT,
    address_line1 VARCHAR(100),
    address_line2 VARCHAR(100),
    city VARCHAR(50),
    state VARCHAR(50),
    postal_code VARCHAR(20)
);

CREATE TABLE bikes (
    bike_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    bike_name VARCHAR(50),
    brand VARCHAR(50),
    type VARCHAR(50),
    price DECIMAL(10, 2),
    year INT
);

CREATE TABLE purchases (
    purchase_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id INT,
    bike_id INT,
    purchase_date DATE,
    quantity INT
);

CREATE TABLE reviews (
    review_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id INT,
    bike_id INT,
    rating INT,
    feedback TEXT
);
